# 🔐 AI-Powered Phishing Detection & Website Safety Analyzer

A machine learning system that detects phishing websites in real-time 
with **96.98% accuracy** — trained on 88,647 real URLs.

## 🚀 Features
- Detects phishing URLs using Random Forest classifier
- Trained on 88,647 real-world URLs (58k legitimate + 30k phishing)
- 112 URL-based features analyzed per site
- Visual confusion matrix and feature importance charts
- Model saved and ready for API deployment

## 📊 Model Performance
| Metric | Score |
|--------|-------|
| Accuracy | 96.98% |
| Precision (Phishing) | 0.95 |
| Recall (Phishing) | 0.96 |
| F1-Score | 0.96 |

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Python, scikit-learn, pandas, numpy
- Random Forest Classifier
- Matplotlib & Seaborn for visualization
- FastAPI (coming soon)
- Chrome Extension (coming soon)

